                "imgDesc": "<p>Balls made of metal that can be grabbed by the Scions of the Canopy using grappling hooks or Yumkasaurs using their own abilities. Once you obtain one, <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Hold </span>to aim and <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Release </span>to fire.<br>If the ball flies onto a metal platform, that platform will activate.<br>However, these balls will not vanish, unlike real Relay Balls, so they can be removed from platforms that they are not locked to and re-used.</p>",
